OL,3,GHighlands & Eilean Siar
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FSunny spells and a touch of
OL,6,Ffrost first thing in the morning for
OL,7,Fsome. Turning rather cloudy through
OL,8,Fthe day, patchy rain arriving in west,
OL,9,Fbut mainly dry in east.
OL,10,
OL,11,CTonight:FA rather cloudy evening with
OL,12,Fa few showery bands of rain spreading
OL,13,Fnortheast. Some drier and clearer
OL,14,Fspells will then develop during the
OL,15,Frest of the night. Freshening
OL,16,Fsoutherly winds.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
