OL,2,W+.-'"-$/*%*%*%/"-$/*%Q,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,3,GHighlands & Eilean Siar
OL,4,
OL,5,CThursday:FPartly cloudy with showery
OL,6,Foutbreaks of rain, some may be on the
OL,7,Fheavy side in the west. Drier,
OL,8,Fbrighter around the Moray Firth.
OL,9,FRather breezy, occasionally strong on
OL,10,Fwest coast.
OL,11,
OL,12,COutlook for Friday to Sunday:FA good
OL,13,Fdeal of dry weather during this period
OL,14,Fwith variable amounts of cloud.
OL,15,FHowever a few showers or spells of
OL,16,Frain can't be ruled out.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
